	(text "XTAL1/CLKIN PIN CAN BE USED AS A CLK INPUT FOR ADS1255\nTHIS WAS ALREADY TESTED WITH AN ESP32 GENERATING A \n7.8MHZ CLOCK AND ADS1255 WORKS GOOD. TAKE INTO ACCOUNT\nTHIS OPTION IF YOU WISH TO AVOID THE XTAL OPTION\n"
