	(text "I PERSONALLY RECOMMEND TO FOLLOW ADS1255 DATASHEET'S \nRECOMMENDATION FOR CRYSTALS. AS I HAVE EXPERIENCED TROUBLE\nTRYING TO GET A GENERIC 8 MHZ CRYSTAL TO WORKS.\nPCB LAYOUT DOENS'T SEEMS PROBLEMATIC TO MY UNDERSTANDING.\nYOU CAN ALSO CHECK THE APPLICATION REPORT SBAA104 FROM\nTEXAS INSTRUMENTS CALLED \n\"Using Ceramic Resonators with the ADS1255/6\""
		(exclude_from_sim no)
